Subject: [PATCH] arm64: configs: rockchip_defconfig: enable mailbox and scpi

This adds select mailbox and scpi support.

Change-Id: I98fa6ee1ca210779b44c1351b68e8725071de07a
Signed-off-by: Frank Wang <frank.wang@rock-chips.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/rockchip_defconfig | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/rockchip_defconfig b/arch/arm64/configs/rockchip_defconfig
index 927e49c6ee24..81dc408fb768 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/rockchip_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/rockchip_defconfig
@@ -648,6 +648,8 @@ CONFIG_RK_CONSOLE_THREAD=y
 CONFIG_COMMON_CLK_RK808=y
 # CONFIG_COMMON_CLK_XGENE is not set
 CONFIG_MAILBOX=y
+CONFIG_RK3368_MBOX=y
+CONFIG_RK3368_SCPI_PROTOCOL=y
 CONFIG_ROCKCHIP_IOMMU=y
 CONFIG_RK_IOMMU=y
 CONFIG_RK_IOVMM=y
